.\" ****************************************************************************
.\" * Exit codes                                                               *
.\" ****************************************************************************
.SH "EXIT CODES"

Possible exit codes are: 
.IP 0 
Success.
.IP 1
Fatal error. Upstream site updated or unexpected result.
.IP 2
No available module (provided module name does not exist).
.IP 3
Network error. Mostly curl related.
.IP 4
Site login failed.
.IP 8
System generic error.
.TP
If plowup is invoked with multiple links or a link-list file and if one or several errors occur, the first error code is returned added with 100.

